<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/card.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/post-grid.css" />

    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/navbar.css" /> -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <style>
      .active { color: orangered !important; font-weight: bold !important; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- NAV -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-body-tertiary">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/Day 10/index.html">
          <img
            src="/assets/picture/logo-dumbways.png"
            style="width: 50px"
            alt="image here"
          />
        </a>

        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-bs-toggle="collapse"
          data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-label="Toggle navigation"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
          <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
            </li>

            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="/blog">Add Project</a>
            </li>

            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="testimonial">Testimonial</a>
            </li>
          </ul>

          {{#if user}}
            <h3 style="margin-right: 30px; color:orangered">Hello,
              {{user.name}}</h3>
            <a
              style="margin-right: 10px;"
              href="/logout"
              class="btn btn-outline-danger"
            >Logout</a>
          {{else}}
            <a
              style="margin-right: 10px;"
              href="/register"
              class="btn btn-outline-warning"
            >Register</a>
            <a
              style="margin-right: 10px;"
              href="/login"
              class="btn btn-outline-warning"
            >Login</a>
          {{/if}}

          <a href="contact" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Contact Me</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- NAV -->

    {{#if messages.error}}
      <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
        {{messages.error}}
      </div>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if messages.success}}
      <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
        {{messages.success}}
      </div>
    {{/if}}

    <!-- CARD -->
    <div class="card-container">
      <div class="card">
        <img
          src="https://static.promediateknologi.id/crop/0x0:0x0/0x0/webp/photo/p2/74/2024/07/08/1716888614661_IMG_3205-3135610797.jpeg"
          alt="ini gambar"
          class="card-img"
        />
        <h2>{{user.name}}</h2>
        <h5>{{user.email}}</h5>
        <p>{{user.createdAt}}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <h1>HELLO WORLD!</h1>
        <p>
          In an increasingly interconnected world, communication and
          collaboration have become the cornerstones of success across
          industries. The ability to effectively share ideas, work together
          toward common goals, and build relationships is critical in both
          personal and professional contexts. With the rise of digital
          platforms, individuals and businesses now have unprecedented access to
          global networks, enabling them to connect and innovate like never
          before. These advancements have not only transformed the way we
          interact but have also opened up new avenues for growth and
          development. 
        </p>
        <p>
         At the same time, the challenges facing our world have
          become more complex, from climate change and resource depletion to
          economic inequalities and geopolitical tensions. Addressing these
          issues requires creative solutions and collective action from people
          across cultures and disciplines. As we navigate this dynamic
          landscape, there is a growing recognition of the need for
          sustainability, ethical leadership, and responsible innovation. By
          harnessing the power of collaboration and technology, we can work
          together to create a more prosperous and equitable future for all.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br />
    <!-- CARD -->

    <div class="project-title">
      <br />
      <h1>MY PROJECT</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <section class="grid-container">

      {{#if user}}
        {{#each data}}
          <div class="grid-item">
            <div>
              <img src="{{image}}" alt="ini gambar rusak" />
              <a href="/blog-detail/{{id}}"><h3>{{title}}</h3></a>
              <h4 class="content-text1">{{startDate}}
                -
                {{endDate}}
                |
                {{this.user.name}}<br />{{duration}}</h4>
              <div class="card-text1">
                {{content}}
              </div>
              <p class="content-text3">{{technologies}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="post-btn">
              <a
                href="/blog-detail/{{id}}"
                type="button"
                class="btn btn-primary"
              >view</a>

              <a
                href="/edit-blog/{{id}}"
                type="button"
                class="btn btn-success"
              >edit</a>

              <a
                href="/delete-blog/{{id}}"
                type="button"
                class="btn btn-danger"
              >delete</a>

            </div>
          </div>
        {{/each}}

      {{else}}
        {{#each data}}
          <div class="grid-item">
            <div>
              <img src="{{image}}" alt="ini gambar rusak" />
              <a href="/blog-detail/{{id}}"><h3>{{title}}</h3></a>
              <h4 class="content-text1">{{startDate}}
                -
                {{endDate}}<br />{{duration}}</h4>
              <div class="card-text1">
                {{content}}
              </div>
              <p class="content-text3">{{technologies}}</p>
            </div>

            <a
              href="/blog-detail/{{id}}"
              type="button"
              class="btn btn-primary"
            >view</a>
          </div>
        {{/each}}
      {{/if}}

      {{#if user}}
        <div class="grid-item2">
          <a href="add-blog">
            <img
              href="add-blog"
              class="plus-img"
              src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/011/912/003/non_2x/plus-sign-icon-free-png.png"
              alt="Plus"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      {{/if}}

    </section>
    <!-- CONTENT -->

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>